H0.text: Shashlik is what type of food dish. Skewered Meat

H1.text: Shashlik is what type of food dish. Stew

H2.text: Shashlik is what type of food dish. Meatball

H3.text: Shashlik is what type of food dish. Kebob

A4.text: Shashlik is similar to, or sometimes a synonym for, shish kebab.

A5.text: In many English-speaking countries, it refers to the now well-known dish prepared with marinated meat or seafood threaded onto the skewer.
